title: Person of Interest: Shaw VS Hitman
author: POI Fights
comment: Sarah Shahi is great in these action roles. Still, I'd like to see her return to comedic roles.
Watched this episode today, and I love her shoes 😍

I didn't like Shaw at first because who needs another tough New Yorker ethnic girl with a heart of gold; but, they gave the character incredible depth, which is odd because the character can't react emotionally to things.  When she survived the series, I was happy with that choice...
I just love realistic fight scenes
